import React from 'react'
import {Box, ChakraProvider, Container, Stack, Text} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container maxW="100vw" h="100vh" bg="#15202B">
                <Stack direction="row">
                    <Box maxW="300px" h="100vh" bg="tomato"></Box>
                    <Box></Box>
                    <Box></Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Home
